{"tid":1418502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"未買樓既諗清楚 附近有警署壓價先買","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:17:00.000Z","uid":49979,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57eb5ff623e3caf4b9b3bcb3667f972556b9a809","tid":1418502,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:57:48.000Z","msg":"頭先睇立場新聞係TKO live聽記者哥哥聞談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢講左d自己諗法 話以前附近有警署居民會放心<br />\n<br />\n依刻大家都好清楚咩事 到頭先2點半都仲有差佬拖住警犬同居民對屌<br />\n<br />\n見到咁真係好憂心 <br />\n<br />\n而未來popo會愈黎愈惡 定選擇良心發現大家都好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以既然香港既革命之路已經走左出黎 請唔好選擇狗屋附近 係都壓佢老母價<br />\n<br />\nBtw 今日各區大混戰 又記者會之後又老黑斬人<br />\n立場哥哥都話各個記者朋友都已經筋疲力盡 workload都over哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你地 萬二分敬意"},{"pid":"ab1f55b65f1854d63d95ad875274d7ebc8ebc5f7","tid":1418502,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNOxBrP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNOxBrP.gif&h=672c8b5c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bDJNqkb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbDJNqkb.gif&h=27f2be48&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSSP , 06/08 , mid-night<br />\n行過想拉就拉"},{"pid":"788083abf99d8fc2a50b3895a03cc0d4ac7c064d","tid":1418502,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87144f35d395392aa2c68482316ce5f118045a71","tid":1418502,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606a8cf03f097cbbe5d2b49e5df270ac4f123216","tid":1418502,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim